OL,3,CIreland rugby star Jack Kyle to be
OL,4,Ccommemorated with blue plaque
OL,6,FJack Kyle, voted Ireland's greatest
OL,7,Fever rugby player, is to be
OL,8,Fcommemorated with an Ulster History
OL,9,FCircle Blue Plaque at the Affidea
OL,10,FStadium in Belfast.
OL,12,FKyle was key to Ireland's
OL,13,Finternational success in the postwar
OL,14,Fera, including a first-ever Grand
OL,15,FSlam, secured at Ravenhill in 1948.
