OL,3,CIreland rugby star Jack Kyle to be
OL,4,Ccommemorated with blue plaque
OL,6,FAlready playing for Ulster, he made
OL,7,Fhis first appearance for Ireland and
OL,8,Fscored a try at the age of 19, playing
OL,9,Fthe British Army XV in an unofficial
OL,10,Finternational at Ravenhill in December
OL,11,F1945.
OL,13,FOne commentator described him as "the
OL,14,Fdiscovery of the season... a pale,
OL,15,Ffreckled medical student with crinkly
OL,16,Fginger hair".
OL,18,FKyle's first cap in an official
OL,19,Finternational was against France in
OL,20,F1947.
