OL,3,CIreland rugby star Jack Kyle to be
OL,4,Ccommemorated with blue plaque
OL,6,FIn 1962 he got a job as a consultant
OL,7,Fsurgeon based in Sumatra in Indonesia
OL,8,Fand a few years later he was in
OL,9,FZambia, in the small mining town of
OL,10,FChingola, not far from the border with
OL,11,Fthe Congo, where he was to spend
OL,12,Falmost 35 years.
OL,14,FIn her book, his daughter Justine Kyle
OL,15,FMcGrath wrote: "So many people during
OL,16,Fmy life have told me how much Dad
OL,17,Fhelped them when they were ill... Many
OL,18,Fpeople have actually told me that if
OL,19,Fit wasn't for dad, they wouldn't be
OL,20,Falive."
