OL,3,CIreland rugby star Jack Kyle to be
OL,4,Ccommemorated with blue plaque
OL,6,FFor his work in Africa, Kyle was given
OL,7,Fa lifetime achievement award by the
OL,8,FIrish Journal of Medical Science and
OL,9,Fthe Royal Academy of Medicine in
OL,10,FIreland.
OL,12,FKyle was inducted into several halls
OL,13,Fof fame, including the Texaco award in
OL,14,F1977, the first rugby player to be
OL,15,Fgiven the honour.
OL,17,FMs Kyle McGrath said her father, who
OL,18,Fdied in 2014, "would have been
OL,19,Fdelighted to receive this honour of a
OL,20,Fblue plaque in his name".
