OL,3,CIreland rugby star Jack Kyle to be
OL,4,Ccommemorated with blue plaque
OL,6,F"It is especially fitting that the
OL,7,Funveiling will take place on what
OL,8,Fwould have been his 100th birthday,"
OL,9,Fshe said.
OL,11,F"It is also meaningful that the plaque
OL,12,Fwill be located at the rugby ground
OL,13,Fwhere dad had so many happy memories."
OL,15,FHugh McCaughey, chief executive of
OL,16,FUlster Rugby, said: "Jack Kyle is one
OL,17,Fof the true giants of Irish and world
OL,18,Frugby, and his legacy continues to
OL,19,Finspire everyone connected with Ulster
OL,20,FRugby.
