OL,3,CIreland rugby star Jack Kyle to be
OL,4,Ccommemorated with blue plaque
OL,6,F"His skill, humility and sportsmanship
OL,7,Fset standards that still define the
OL,8,Fgame today.
OL,10,F"It is entirely fitting that this
OL,11,Fplaque stands here to recognise not
OL,12,Fonly Jack's extraordinary achievements
OL,13,Fon the field, but also his lasting
OL,14,Fimpact on rugby in Ulster and far
OL,15,Fbeyond."
